The lawyer, who cannot be named as he has not yet made an appearance in court, is accused of shooting and wounding four people following a dispute at the farm. The shooting allegedly occurred in Polokwane on Thursday morning. According to reports, the lawyer was then arrested following a manhunt and has since been charged with four counts of attempted murder. Limpopo police confirmed the arrest of the lawyer and he is expected to appear in court on June 23, 2017. IOL